---
title: Sticky Pork Meatballs & Jasmine Rice with Soy Stir-Fry Veggies & Garlic Aioli
description: Sweet chilli and oyster sauce has to be our new favourite flavour combo, and it’s even better turned into a glaze and slathered all over savoury pork meatballs. Don’t let that extra sauce go to waste - soak it up with jasmine rice and spoon it over the garlicky veggies to max out on those delicious flavours!
